Line 209 of AccumulatingProgressMonitor.java from N20041103 is in the middle of
a javadoc comment. The subTask method, where the NPE is reported, has not
changed in two years and looks like this:

    public synchronized void subTask(final String name) {
        if (collector == null) {
            createCollector(name, 0);
        } else {
            collector.subTask(name);
        }
    }

There is no way for an NPE to occur in this method.
